.git
.gitignore
.idea
LICENSE
Dockerfile.*
**/.dockerignore
**/*.md
**/dist
**/node_modules
# Generated DSFR assets (recreated by the web `copy-dsfr-to-public` postinstall in
# the deps stage); excluded so the web install layer's cache key depends only on
# tracked inputs and stays identical between local and CI builds.
apps/web/public/dsfr
**/scalingo
# Allow nginx config from scalingo directory for Docker builds
!apps/web/scalingo/nginx.conf.erb
**/.DS_Store
**/*.local